# Architecture

## Parent / App
- `mall-system` is the parent aggregator project.
- `mall-app` contains only:
  - boot application
  - app-level configuration
  - dependency aggregation

## Shared Modules
- `mall-common`:
  - Result
  - ResultCode
  - BizException
  - GlobalExceptionHandler
  - enums
  - shared constants
- `mall-infra`:
  - jwt
  - redis
  - mybatis config
  - interceptor
  - user context
  - generic infra configs

## Business Modules
- `mall-user`: auth, current user, address
- `mall-product`: category, product, sku, search
- `mall-cart`: add/list/update/delete/check cart
- `mall-order`: submit/list/detail/cancel/status
- `mall-pay`: create pay/callback/result
- `mall-mq`: timeout close / async post-payment consumers

## Layering
- controller -> service -> mapper
- no business logic in controller
- no transaction in controller
